==Useful Info==
'''Sea snakes''' are found in [[the Shoals]] and [[the Snake Pit]], usually lying in ambush in the water. They're quick, beefy, and carry a ''hefty'' [[poison]]ous bite that is only weakened by poison resistance.

==Tips & Tricks==
*Poison resistance reduces their damage output tremendously.

==History==
*As of [[0.12]], they no longer flee when moderately injured.
*Prior to [[0.11]], sea snake poison could not overwhelm rPois.
